data.description:
@beats time on your wrist! Because what's the point of a programmable watchface if not to mess with your perception of time?

@beats is a time system designed by Swatch, which divides the day into 1000 beats. There are no timezones; the @beats time now is the @beats time everywhere around the world.

Based off the excellent code at https://github.com/jerith/pebble-beapoch
